fields.name: IRENA Youth Forum 2026 in UAE (Fully Funded)
fields.description: Are you ready to attend a fully funded youth forum in Abu Dhabi, UAE? Youth from around the world are invited to apply for the 8th Edition of the IRENA Youth Forum 2026. The Forum will run from 8th to 10th January 2026 at the IRENA Assembly. This International Youth Forum is a platform to empower young people to engage and contribute their ideas and solutions to the energy transition. It is organized annually by the International Renewable Energy Agency (IRENA). The theme of the 2026 IRENA Youth Forum is: “Youth Innovation and Digital Solutions: From AI to Access in Renewable Energy.” More details about the benefits and the requirements are below.
fields.benefits:
Benefits for Participants
Upon selection, successful participants will receive:

Travel Tickets
Accommodation
Meals
fields.eligibility:
Eligibility Criteria
Youth between the ages of 16 and 35 years can submit their application.
IELTS is not required.
You must have to apply online.
